OL,3,CKhan: Ministers must end 'everyday
OL,4,Cextortion' of unfair charges for
OL,5,Cleaseholders
OL,7,FLondon Mayor Sadiq Khan is urging
OL,8,Fministers to end the "everyday
OL,9,Fextortion" of unfair service charges
OL,10,Ffor leaseholders.
OL,12,FHe is demanding legal powers for
OL,13,Fleaseholders to withhold service
OL,14,Fcharge payments where the
OL,15,Fjustification has not been set out in
OL,16,Fwriting.
