OL,3,CKhan: Ministers must end 'everyday
OL,4,Cextortion' of unfair charges for
OL,5,Cleaseholders
OL,7,FThe City Hall incumbent's intervention
OL,8,Fcomes less than a week before the May
OL,9,F2 mayoral election in the capital,
OL,10,Fwhere he is seeking a historic third
OL,11,Fterm in office.
OL,13,FHe said: "If leaseholders face large
OL,14,Fincreases in their service charge
OL,15,Fwithout it being clearly explained
OL,16,Fwhat it's paying for, they should be
OL,17,Fable to do something about it `
OL,18,Fincluding having stronger rights in
OL,19,Flaw."
