OL,3,CKhan: Ministers must end 'everyday
OL,4,Cextortion' of unfair charges for
OL,5,Cleaseholders
OL,7,FMr Khan also wants the Government to
OL,8,Fuse the Leasehold and Freehold Reform
OL,9,FBill currently going through
OL,10,FParliament to make it easier for
OL,11,Fleaseholders to take their landlords
OL,12,Fto court to challenge unreasonable
OL,13,Fcosts.
OL,15,FLeaseholders should also get quicker
OL,16,Fredress by expanding the remit of the
OL,17,Fhousing ombudsman to investigate
OL,18,Fservice charge hikes, the mayor argues.
