OL,3,CKhan: Ministers must end 'everyday
OL,4,Cextortion' of unfair charges for
OL,5,Cleaseholders
OL,7,FLeaseholds are a form of home
OL,8,Fownership that gives the householders
OL,9,Fthe right to live in a property for a
OL,10,Ffixed number of years but can also
OL,11,Fmean having to pay service charges to
OL,12,Fthe freeholder, who owns the land.
OL,14,FLondon has 1.4 million leasehold
OL,15,Fproperties, a quarter of all such
OL,16,Fproperties in the country.
