OL,3,CKhan: Ministers must end 'everyday
OL,4,Cextortion' of unfair charges for
OL,5,Cleaseholders
OL,7,FThe Leasehold and Freehold Reform Bill
OL,8,Fhas faced criticism for failing to
OL,9,Foutlaw this housing system branded
OL,10,F"feudal" by Housing Secretary Michael
OL,11,FGove.
OL,13,FWhile the legislation bans the sale of
OL,14,Fnew leasehold houses, except in
OL,15,Fexceptional circumstances, it does not
OL,16,Fban the sale of new leasehold flats,
OL,17,Fwhich make up 70% of properties
OL,18,Faffected.
