OL,3,CKhan: Ministers must end 'everyday
OL,4,Cextortion' of unfair charges for
OL,5,Cleaseholders
OL,7,FAction the Labour London mayor has
OL,8,Ftaken to support leaseholders includes
OL,9,Fintroducing a requirement for 990-year
OL,10,Fleases as standard for shared
OL,11,Fownership homes funded by City Hall.
OL,13,FBut he does not have the power
OL,14,Fregulate existing homes or change
OL,15,Fcurrent legislation, and so is urging
OL,16,Fministers to act, upping the pressure
OL,17,Fon Mr Gove who has already been
OL,18,Faccused of heavily diluting the Bill.
