OL,3,CKhan: Ministers must end 'everyday
OL,4,Cextortion' of unfair charges for
OL,5,Cleaseholders
OL,7,FMr Khan said: "Sky-high service
OL,8,Fcharges can be financially crippling
OL,9,Ffor people living in flats or who are
OL,10,Fshared owners. At their worst, they
OL,11,Famount to the everyday extortion of
OL,12,Fleaseholders and a shameful abuse of
OL,13,Fpower by landlords and freeholders.
OL,15,F"While many landlords act responsibly,
OL,16,Fwe need stronger rights for
OL,17,Fleaseholders to act against those who
OL,18,Fdon't, with new powers of redress and
OL,19,Fthe ability to withhold service
OL,20,Fcharges that simply aren't justified."
