OL,3,CKhan: Ministers must end 'everyday
OL,4,Cextortion' of unfair charges for
OL,5,Cleaseholders
OL,7,FHe added: "I'll keep campaigning for
OL,8,Fthe end of our current system of
OL,9,Fleasehold ownership, and the
OL,10,Fintroduction of commonhold as the new
OL,11,Fdefault tenure for flat owners in
OL,12,FLondon and across the country."
OL,14,FHe also described Conservative rival
OL,15,FSusan Hall as a "hard-right Tory
OL,16,Fcandidate who will never stand up to
OL,17,Fvested interests in the property
OL,18,Fmarket".
