OL,4,Cextortion' of unfair charges for
OL,5,Cleaseholders
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,8,FLevelling Up, Housing and Communities
OL,9,Fsaid: "Unjustified increases in
OL,10,Fservice charges are completely
OL,11,Funacceptable, which is why we are
OL,12,Fcommitted to strengthening protection
OL,13,Ffor leaseholders, and are bringing
OL,14,Fforward reforms through the Leasehold
OL,15,Fand Freehold Reform Bill. This will
OL,16,Fempower them and make it easier to
OL,17,Fchallenge unfair costs."
